File: cmd/gophkeeper-server/main.go
Package: main
Scope: Exported
Role: Entrypoint
Purpose: Initializes server configuration and executes the root CLI command for the GophKeeper storage server application.

Functions:
func main(). Purpose: Entrypoint flow. Initializes Viper configuration via config.NewViper, constructs server root command tree via commands.NewServerRootCommand, and triggers arguments parsing and execution loop via rootCmd.Execute. Errors: logs fatal on command initialization failure; exits with code 1 on command execution failure.
